# {{ project_name }}

A [Mistral Workflows](https://docs.mistral.ai/capabilities/workflows/) project.

## Setup

```bash
uv sync
```

## Commands

### Register workflows in AI Studio

Auto-discovers all workflow classes in `src/workflows/`, registers them with AI Studio, and starts polling for executions. The task queue is set to your hostname:

```bash
make register
```

### Trigger a workflow execution

In a separate terminal, trigger an execution of the hello workflow:

```bash
make start
```

## Development

```bash
# Format
uv run ruff format .

# Lint
uv run ruff check --fix .
```
